&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Software Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About CoVar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;TextRun SCXW180583606 BCX0&quot; lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;NormalTextRun SCXW180583606 BCX0&quot;&gt;CoVar is a small, mission-driven AI/ML R&amp;amp;D software company based in Durham, NC and McLean, VA. We build advanced software and machine learning systems that help the Department of Defense detect threats in high-stakes environments and enable biomedical researchers to accelerate discoveries that save lives. Our team is composed of curious, passionate engineers who care deeply about using AI to solve real-world problems that matter.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About this position&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We&amp;nbsp;are looking for a motivated, detail-oriented Software Engineer who thrives in an environment where reading, understanding, and improving complex codebases is just as important as writing new code. In this role, you will develop and&amp;nbsp;maintain&amp;nbsp;real-time, computationally intensive applications involving data processing, real-time communications, and machine-learning algorithm integration.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;You’ll&amp;nbsp;work closely with a team of ML engineers and software developers, contribute to system architecture and performance optimization, and help ensure our tools are robust, efficient, and production ready.&amp;nbsp;You will have the opportunity to work on meaningful, high-impact projects in a close-knit engineering team.&amp;nbsp;If you enjoy building systems end-to-end,&amp;nbsp;optimizing&amp;nbsp;performance, and understanding how software interacts with hardware at a deep level,&amp;nbsp;you’ll&amp;nbsp;fit right in.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:6}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
